text: Hello. Does development sandbox have a price?

What would you like to embed if you had that option?

I strongly believe the breadcrumb at the top here is completely miss built. (first screenshot)

If you want a breadcrumb here it should be for the placement of the module, e.g. contents>section>column>module name (though this isn’t necessary just as none of the other parts have a bread crumb e.g. Add to page, Optimise etc)

There should be a seperate module breadcrumb below smart rules which only lists the groups you’re in within your module having to navigate above the module title is not intuitive and a bad UX further the inclusion of “contents” means the breadcrumb regularly has to be elipsissed.

The design manager makes it so much more simple (second screenshot)
